# Product Specification: EmbedKit

**Related documents:** [project-conventions.mdc](../.cursor/rules/project-conventions.mdc), [task.mdc](./task.mdc)

## 1. Product Overview

### Name

**EmbedKit** — a no-code platform for building document-grounded AI chatbots with in-app testing and a website embed widget.

**Tagline:** *Turn your docs into a chatbot. Embed it on your site in minutes.*

### Positioning

EmbedKit is a lightweight self-serve builder positioned between a basic FAQ widget and an enterprise helpdesk platform.

| Segment | Limitation | EmbedKit response |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| Intercom Fin | Requires Intercom; complex onboarding; per-resolution pricing | Standalone product; fast setup; flat pricing |
| CustomGPT | High accuracy at scale; higher price point | Focus on speed and simplicity for SMB use cases |
| Chatbase | Fast setup; branding and API behind paywall | Clear tier structure; paywall after demonstrated value |

### Target Audience

**Primary (MVP)**

- **SMB / micro-SaaS** (5–50 employees): founders, product marketers, or support leads who need a FAQ/support bot without engineering resources.
- **Support teams** at growing SaaS companies: first-line self-serve before escalation to Intercom or Zendesk.

**Secondary (post-MVP)**

- Agencies building bots for clients (white-label on Business tier).
- Internal knowledge teams converting HR/ops wikis into employee-facing chat.

### Personas

| Persona | Role | Problem | Expected outcome |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| Alex, Founder | CEO, micro-SaaS | Support consumes founder time; no budget for Intercom | Launch a pricing/docs FAQ bot quickly |
| Maya, Support Lead | Head of Support, SaaS | Repetitive questions in Slack and email | Bot with help-center citations and site embed |
| Jordan, Product Marketer | PMM | Needs a branded chat experience on the marketing site | Branded widget without platform watermark |

### Jobs to Be Done

1. When I have PDFs, docs, or FAQs, I want to turn them into a chatbot so I can answer customers 24/7 without hiring.
2. When the bot is ready, I want to add a single embed snippet to my site so I do not depend on developers.
3. When I confirm the bot works, I want to remove the watermark and apply my brand so the experience looks professional to customers.

