## 2. Competitive References

Reference products are used to identify proven interaction patterns. UI must not be copied verbatim. Relevant Mobbin flow categories: Onboarding, Chat Bot, Subscription & Paywall, Account Setup.

### Intercom Fin

**Observed patterns**

- **Train → Preview → Deploy:** content ingestion, validation, then publication.
- **Unified knowledge hub:** articles, PDFs, URLs, and snippets in one place with per-source AI enablement.
- **Inline preview** adjacent to content list for pre-deploy testing.
- **Guidance layer** separate from content: tone, policies, escalation rules.
- **Deploy separated from Train:** going live is an explicit user action.

**Adopted for EmbedKit:** preview before deploy; separate Knowledge and Deploy areas; contextual paywall when removing branding or enabling production embed.

**Excluded:** workflow builder, omnichannel deployment, enterprise pricing complexity.

### Chatbase

**Observed patterns**

- **Short setup loop:** upload → customize widget → copy embed → go live.
- **Data sources tab** with files, website crawl, and Q&A pairs; real-time processing status.
- **Deploy tab** with widget on/off toggle and ready-made `<script>` snippet.
- **Widget customization:** bubble icon, colors, welcome message, suggested questions.
- **Separate upsell triggers** for branding removal and API access.

**Adopted for EmbedKit:** fast onboarding, copy-paste deploy, suggested starter questions, contextual upgrade on watermark removal.

**Excluded:** per-message credits as primary UX metric; omnichannel.

### CustomGPT

**Observed patterns**

- **Project-centric dashboard:** one project equals one bot with its own knowledge base.
- **Built-in test chat:** full ChatGPT-style interface before external embed.
- **Source attribution:** citations and document references in responses.
- **Tiered limits** on documents and agents across Free → Standard → Premium.

**Adopted for EmbedKit:** in-app test chat as a core screen; source citations in responses; document limits as a paywall lever.

**Excluded:** 1400+ file formats, enterprise SSO, auto-sync integrations in MVP.

### Pattern Adoption Matrix

| Pattern | Intercom Fin | Chatbase | CustomGPT | EmbedKit MVP |
| :--- | :---: | :---: | :---: | :---: |
| Upload docs → train | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes |
| In-app test chat | Preview | Yes | Yes | Yes |
| Embed code snippet | Messenger | Yes | Yes | Yes |
| Widget customization | Yes | Yes | Yes | Pro |
| Source citations | Yes | Partial | Yes | Yes (mocked) |
| Paywall after value demonstration | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes |
| Team seats | Yes | Yes | Yes | Business |
| API access | Yes | Standard+ | Yes | Business |

