## 5. User Stories

### Discovery and Landing

- **US-01:** As a visitor, I want to understand the product within 10 seconds so I can decide whether to sign up.
- **US-02:** As a visitor, I want to see a widget preview on the landing page so I can envision the result on my site.

### Authentication and Setup

- **US-03:** As a new user, I want to sign up with email or Google without a credit card so I can start immediately.
- **US-04:** As a user, I want to name my bot and set an avatar so it reflects my brand.
- **US-05:** As a user, I want to upload up to 5 documents via drag-and-drop so I can train my bot on the Free plan.

### Knowledge and Chat

- **US-06:** As a user, I want to see processing status for each document so I know when testing is available.
- **US-07:** As a user, I want to ask questions in a ChatGPT-style interface so I can validate answer quality before deploy.
- **US-08:** As a user, I want to see the source of each answer so I can trust bot responses.
- **US-09:** As a user, I want to click suggested questions so I can quickly test common scenarios.

### Widget and Deploy

- **US-10:** As a user, I want to configure widget colors and welcome message with live preview so the widget matches my site.
- **US-11:** As a user, I want to copy embed code in one click so I can add the widget without developers.
- **US-12:** As a Free user, I want to see the watermark in preview so I understand what changes after upgrade.

### Paywall and Billing

- **US-13:** As a Free user, I want a contextual upgrade prompt when removing the watermark so I understand Pro value.
- **US-14:** As a user, I want to compare plans side by side so I can select the appropriate tier.
- **US-15:** As a Pro user, I want analytics (conversations, top questions) so I can improve my knowledge base.

### Business Tier

- **US-16:** As a Business user, I want to create multiple bots for different products or clients.
- **US-17:** As a Business user, I want to invite teammates so support and marketing can collaborate.
- **US-18:** As a Business user, I want an API key so I can integrate the bot into my product.

