## 7. MVP Scope

This project delivers a clickable prototype. No backend is required.

### In Scope

- Landing page with onboarding CTA
- Authentication screens (mocked)
- Full builder flow: upload → chat → widget → embed
- Paywall modal and pricing page with gated UI states
- Micro-interactions: upload progress, typing indicator, copy-to-clipboard confirmation
- Mock chat responses with citations (fixed response set; one response minimum)

### Out of Scope

- RAG or LLM pipeline
- Real authentication and billing (Stripe)
- Functional embed script (preview and snippet UI only)
- Omnichannel deployment
- API documentation
- Team invitation flow (placeholder UI permitted)
- Public share link for bots

---

## 8. Brand and Design Requirements

### Voice and Copy

- Direct and confident: *Your docs, answering 24/7* — not generic AI marketing language.
- Action-oriented labels: *Copy code*, *Test your bot*, *Add a document*.
- Explicit plan limits: *Free plan includes EmbedKit watermark*.

### Visual Direction

- Clean SaaS aesthetic; avoid generic AI gradient templates.
- Single accent color (teal or coral); warm gray neutrals.
- Widget preview renders as a realistic floating bubble, not a wireframe.
- Motion: message fade-in, upload progress, confirmation on first embed copy.

### UI Component Inventory

| Component | Location | Specification |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `ChatMessage` | Test chat, widget preview | User and assistant bubbles; citation chips |
| `SuggestedQuestions` | Chat empty state | Three clickable pills |
| `DocumentUploadZone` | Knowledge | Drag-and-drop; file list; processing badge |
| `WidgetPreview` | Widget builder | Live embed mock |
| `EmbedCodeBlock` | Deploy | Syntax highlighting; copy button |
| `PaywallModal` | Gated actions | Plan comparison; upgrade CTA |
| `PlanBadge` | Navigation, settings | Free / Pro / Business indicator |
| `UpgradeBanner` | Gated screens | Inline; dismissible |

