## 9. Success Metrics

Post-launch targets. Not applicable to the prototype itself.

| Metric | Definition | Target |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| Activation rate | Signed up → uploaded ≥1 document | > 60% |
| Aha rate | Uploaded → sent ≥1 test message | > 70% |
| Embed rate | Aha → copied embed code | > 40% |
| Free → Pro conversion | Upgrade within 14 days | > 5% |
| Time to first answer | Sign-up → first bot response | < 5 min |

